# Rename-dance leftovers (v1.7.13+ self-updater intermediates that live
# next to displayoff.exe in the install dir — usually cleaned by
# _recover_from_failed_update on next launch, but defensive against any
# .exe.old / .exe.tmp ever landing in the repo via build/ tinkering).
# v1.7.17: narrowed `*.old` (which shadowed legitimate `.old` files
# anywhere in the tree, like backup notes or test fixtures) to the two
# specific rename-dance patterns. Any future updater intermediate gets
# its own explicit line here.
*.exe.old
*.exe.tmp

# Python
__pycache__/
*.pyc
.venv/
venv/
*.egg-info/

# Config (may contain personal paths)
*.cfg
displayoff_config.json

# Environment
.env

