CLAUDE.md

# swarmaudit artifacts (audit cache, never publish)
.swarmaudit/

# Nuitka build artifacts (v1.7.13+ frozen .exe build dir + crash reports)
# build/ holds the displayoff.dist + displayoff.onefile-build + displayoff.exe
# from `bash build-release.sh` or `build-exe.bat`. The .exe gets uploaded
# as a release asset; the build dir is local-only scratch.
build/
